Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.02,0:22:27.20,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}見つけたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.20,0:22:30.31,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}幸せってやつを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.61,0:22:35.20,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}君がくれた世界で僕は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.20,0:22:38.17,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}たったひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.17,0:22:42.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}君を想うだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.52,0:22:47.26,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}あんなに輝いて見えたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:49.81,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}何度でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.81,0:22:54.76,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}言葉にして見せるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.76,0:23:02.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}君が僕のこと忘れてしまったとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:06.68,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}また胸の奥で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.68,0:23:09.70,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}交わした約束が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.70,0:23:13.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}響き合うように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.18,0:23:18.57,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}ああ、目を開ければ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.57,0:23:23.21,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}君のいない世界が始まる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:27.67,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}今でも瞼の裏側
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:30.72,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}ちらつく雨の中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.72,0:23:35.09,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}いつだって君がいるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:41.51,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,500)\blur2}滲んだ世界で君が笑う
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.02,0:22:27.20,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}我終於找到
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.20,0:22:30.31,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}所謂的幸福
Dialogue: 1,0:22:30.61,0:22:35.20,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}在你為我創造的世界裡
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.20,0:22:38.17,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}我只惦念著一個人
Dialogue: 1,0:22:38.17,0:22:42.52,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}我只惦念著你
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.52,0:22:47.26,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}世界就變得如此閃亮
Dialogue: 1,0:22:47.63,0:22:49.81,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}一遍又一遍
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.81,0:22:54.76,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}我願不斷訴說
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.76,0:23:02.07,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}就算我早已在你記憶中褪色
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.07,0:23:06.68,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}讓沉寂在心底
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.68,0:23:09.70,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}你我曾經的約定
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.70,0:23:13.18,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}再次得到喚醒
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.18,0:23:18.57,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}啊 睜開眼睛
Dialogue: 1,0:23:18.57,0:23:23.21,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}又得面對沒有你的世界
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.21,0:23:27.67,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}每當閉上眼眸
Dialogue: 1,0:23:27.67,0:23:30.72,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}或在瀟瀟雨間
Dialogue: 1,0:23:30.72,0:23:35.09,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur2}仍有你的身影
Dialogue: 1,0:23:36.51,0:23:41.51,ED2-CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(250,500)}微笑在這迷濛的世界
